Introduction

Yoon Seo Ryeong (Korean: 윤서령) is a South Korean singer who debuted as a member of the female duo The Two Sisters under JG Star Entertainment in 2021. She is the daughter of Yoon Taekyung, a well-known trot singer in South Korea. Her debut single, “You Know What I’m Talking About”, was released on September 7, 2021.
